/**
 * @file
 * Community chrome + schema tooltips for the Groups demo (CH-F1, #79).
 *
 * This module is the FOUNDATION for the epic #78 tooltip surfaces. It bundles
 * a tooltip library (tippy.js + @popperjs/core) LOCALLY — no external CDN — and
 * establishes an extensible #[Hook] structure so each future tooltip surface
 * (#88-#92) is a single self-contained hook method plus one entry in the
 * centralized copy source (\Drupal\do_chrome\HelpText).
 *
 * All hook implementations live in DoChromeHooks via the #[Hook] attribute.
 *
 * @see \Drupal\do_chrome\Hook\DoChromeHooks
 * @see \Drupal\do_chrome\HelpText
 */
